query:
SELECT g.id, g.playerId, g.matchId, p.name as playerName, t.name as teamName, c.name as campaignName
FROM goals g
JOIN players p ON g.playerId = p.id
JOIN teams t ON p.teamId = t.id
JOIN campaigns c ON t.campaignId = c.id
WHERE c.slug = 'tufao'
LIMIT 10;
